(2730, 552, 'album_details', '<p>Red Bull Studio''s Cape Town asked me to do a mix of my favourite summertimes tunes.<br />\r\nGo to my soundcloud for the free download.</p>\r\n<p>Track Listing here:</p>\r\n<p>1.  Kid Fonque Skit<br />\r\n2.  Kid Fonque ft. Nia Andrews - What I Do (Eric Lau Remix)<br />\r\n3.  Slakah The Beatchild - Stompthatflo ft. Spek Won<br />\r\n4.  Moods - Distance<br />\r\n5.  Kid Fonque - Bossa Over?<br />\r\n6.  Bruce Loko - Peace Within<br />\r\n7.  Kid Fonque &#038; D-Malice ft. Clara Hill - All This Time<br />\r\n8.  Lay-Far with Souled &#038; Yannah Valdevit - Can’t Deny (Phil Asher Remix)<br />\r\n9.  Jonny Miller ft. Lastee - Believe (Jonny’s Dream Dub)<br />\r\n10. Kid Fonque, Okmalumkoolkat, Andy Boi, Jonny Miller, Cuebur - Usangikhumbula<br />\r\n11. Beebar - Angel In Love (Kid Fonque Remix)<br />\r\n12. Amp Live - 100 000 Watts<br />\r\n13. Jumping Back Slash - Boy (Thinking About You)<br />\r\n14. Kid Fonque Outro</p>\r\n'),
