(299, 1, '2014-06-17 09:44:27', '2014-06-17 07:44:27', '<h2>BIOGRAPHY</h2>\r\n<img class="aligncenter wp-image-280 size-full" src="http://www.kidfonque.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/IMG_5911-Edit2.jpg" alt="IMG_5911-Edit2" width="100%" />\r\n\r\nRestless as a DJ and adventurous in the studio, Kid Fonque is a key player in the South African music scene and fresh new presence on the global stage. With his distinctive style and wide-ranging taste, he’s had a vital impact on electronic music locally, and now he’s turning heads around the world.\r\n\r\nWell respected for his eclectic taste, Kid Fonque spent many years honing his skills in South Africa’s electronic music scene before stepping into the studio where his natural flare sparked global attention.\r\n\r\nHis breakthrough as an artist is reflected in recognition via several chart-topping singles which garnered praise from the world’s leading tastemakers (Gilles Peterson, King Britt, DJ Cam, Osunlade – to name a few) and catapulted him into the global club and festival circuit where he recently completed gigs and tours in Switzerland, Hong Kong, London, Berlin and Amsterdam.\r\n\r\nJust as his DJing style melds the explorative and the unexpected, so too do his productions and with the talent to match his diverse and adventurous style - he approaches music-making with newfound confidence and artistic distinction.\r\n\r\nBreaking borders with his inspired sonic escapades., Keep your ears and eyes locked on Kid Fonque!\r\n\r\n<a title="Click here" href="http://www.kidfonque.co.za/biography.pdf">Click here</a> to download my biography.', 'Bio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '211-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-17 09:44:27', '2014-06-17 07:44:27', '', 211, 'http://www.kidfonque.co.za/211-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
